  "content": "<p data-pid=\"1n9LpXXr\">如果没有<b>理性</b>运作的理论——或者其「理论」仅仅与一些含糊不清的老生常谈挂钩，没有精确的解释机制——那么，这种对非理性的陈述也是不完整的。《注意到困惑》系列提出了为什么在「理性」预期的基础上行动会有用，以及在如此行事时会有什么感觉。</p><p data-pid=\"RmlVMSR_\">——<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Biases-An-Introduction\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《偏见：序言》</a><sup data-text=\"偏见（偏差）[5]：导读\" data-url=\"https://hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_0/\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>by Rob Bensinger</p><hr/><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_20/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">集中你的不确定性 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_21/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">什么是证据？ - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_22/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">科学证据，法律证据，理性证据 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_23/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">支持一个信念需要多少证据？ - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_24/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">爱因斯坦的傲慢 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_25/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">奥卡姆剃刀 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_26/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">作为理性主义者的力量 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_27/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">没有证据表明=证据表明没有 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_28/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">证据期望值守恒论 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_29/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">后见之明贬低科学价值 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><hr/><p data-pid=\"Gpq3vNpp\">上一篇：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_19/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">掌声提示光 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><p data-pid=\"sAH9ou4q\">下一篇：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_20/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">集中你的不确定性 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><hr/><blockquote data-pid=\"4JfHdz3u\">HPMOR 翻译组译制<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Noticing-Confusion-Sequence\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Noticing Confusion - Sequence</a></blockquote>",
